After registering, I receive an email:
 - from webmaster@example.org
 - named &#x27;webmaster&#x27;
 - subject &#x27;Welcome OJFord&#x27;
 - signed off &#x27;Regards, The Team&#x27;<p>That is, it does not at all identify where it came from. The example.org sender is particularly odd, I don&#x27;t know why you&#x27;re doing that?
